item.description:
Saw stuff about &ldquo;caste discrimination is pervasive&rdquo; among indian americans on my TL&hellip;to my knowledge, this is a total fabrication. i&rsquo;ve said enough negative things about how some indians/browns behave in the west&hellip;i don&rsquo;t hold back, but i dislike lies a lot.
I condensed most of the important points in my blog post, but to review&hellip;
Most ppl of brown origin are skewed to the &rsquo;elite&rsquo;, and indian hindus are mostly &lsquo;upper caste.
